#. <section class="sutta" id="an10.82"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.82:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.82:0.2"
msgid "9. Theravagga"
msgstr "9. Senior Mendicants"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.82:0.3"
msgid "82. Ānandasutta"
msgstr "82. With Ānanda"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an10.82:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā ānando yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ "
"abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ "
"bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Venerable Ānanda went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat down to one "
"side. The Buddha said to him:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an10.82:2.1"
msgid ""
"“So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘assaddho samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ "
"virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. (1)"
msgstr ""
"“Ānanda, it’s not possible for a faithless mendicant to achieve growth, "
"improvement, or maturity in this teaching and training."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an10.82:3.1"
msgid ""
"So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘dussīlo samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ "
"vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. (2)"
msgstr "It’s not possible for a mendicant who is unethical …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an10.82:4.1"
msgid ""
"So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘appassuto samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ "
"virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. (3)"
msgstr "uneducated …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.153"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an10.82:5.1"
msgid ""
"So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘dubbaco samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ "
"vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. (4)"
msgstr "hard to admonish …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an10.82:6.1"
msgid ""
"So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘pāpamitto samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ "
"virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. (5)"
msgstr "with bad friends …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an10.82:7.1"
msgid ""
"So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘kusīto samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ "
"vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. (6)"
msgstr "lazy …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an10.82:8.1"
msgid ""
"So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘muṭṭhassati samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ "
"virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. (7)"
msgstr "unmindful …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an10.82:9.1"
msgid ""
"So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘asantuṭṭho samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ "
"virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. (8)"
msgstr "lacking contentment …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an10.82:10.1"
msgid ""
"So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘pāpiccho samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ "
"vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. (9)"
msgstr "of bad desires …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "an10.82:11.1"
msgid ""
"So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘micchādiṭṭhiko samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ "
"virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. (10)"
msgstr ""
"of wrong view to achieve growth, improvement, or maturity in this teaching "
"and training."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "an10.82:12.1"
msgid ""
"So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘imehi dasahi dhammehi samannāgato imasmiṃ "
"dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""
"It’s not possible for a mendicant with these ten qualities to achieve "
"growth, improvement, or maturity in this teaching and training."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "an10.82:13.1"
msgid ""
"So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘saddho samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ "
"vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati. (1)"
msgstr ""
"It is possible for a faithful mendicant to achieve growth, improvement, or "
"maturity in this teaching and training."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "an10.82:14.1"
msgid ""
"So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘sīlavā samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ "
"vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati. (2)"
msgstr "It is possible for a mendicant who is ethical …"

# I’m not sure if BB overlooked sutadhara or if he didn’t think it needed translating.
#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "an10.82:15.1"
msgid ""
"So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘bahussuto sutadharo samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye "
"vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati. (3)"
msgstr "a learned memorizer …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "an10.82:16.1"
msgid ""
"So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘suvaco samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ "
"vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati. (4)"
msgstr "easy to admonish …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc17"></a>
msgctxt "an10.82:17.1"
msgid ""
"So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘kalyāṇamitto samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ "
"virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati. (5)"
msgstr "with good friends …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc18"></a>
msgctxt "an10.82:18.1"
msgid ""
"So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘āraddhavīriyo samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ "
"virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati. (6)"
msgstr "energetic …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.154"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc19"></a>
msgctxt "an10.82:19.1"
msgid ""
"So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘upaṭṭhitassati samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ "
"virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati. (7)"
msgstr "mindful …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc20"></a>
msgctxt "an10.82:20.1"
msgid ""
"So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘santuṭṭho samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ "
"virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati. (8)"
msgstr "contented …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc21"></a>
msgctxt "an10.82:21.1"
msgid ""
"So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘appiccho samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ "
"vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati. (9)"
msgstr "of few desires …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc22"></a>
msgctxt "an10.82:22.1"
msgid ""
"So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘sammādiṭṭhiko samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ "
"virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati. (10)"
msgstr ""
"of right view to achieve growth, improvement, or maturity in this teaching "
"and training."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc23"></a>
msgctxt "an10.82:23.1"
msgid ""
"So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘imehi dasahi dhammehi samannāgato imasmiṃ "
"dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"It is possible for a mendicant with these ten qualities to achieve growth, "
"improvement, or maturity in this teaching and training.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.82:23.2"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
